Text: TNGHT is pretty good trap x pop-indie..but uh, if you want straight up trap go find yourself just Lunice's EPs, "Ruff Sqwad - White Label Classics", Flosstradamus, Carnage, Crystal Castles, Crizzly, etc etc...this good starter torrent.
Yeah if anything most of the tracks I picked out were just the most accessible & easiest to start out with instead of delving head first into the genre.
